           name="Культ Исиды (2)"
           tier="2"
           text="{=InFa.fac_banu_qatal.desc}The Banu Qatal is a very, very old clan which lived its prime together with the establishment of the Aserai Sultanate. The Qatals serve the Aserai Sultan as assassins, they were known as the best ones at that, in all of Calradia. It is thought that, they even had a stake in the death of the great Emperor Arenicos. But since then, the clan was on it's downfall, it got infested with traitors and spies. The Sultan of the Aserai had started an act and intervened to clean out the clan. They arrested and executed every spy they found, even most of the other hashashins who were thought to be enemies, got imprisoned. And the rest of the clan, the experienced ones got forced to retire. Today the clan lost a lot of power, and almost destroyed itself.">
