           tier="4"
           text="{=InFa.fac_swordsister.desc}The Sword Sisters are a community of girls who were forced to leave their homes for various reasons. Many girls of Calradia see them as their last hope for sanctuary, when they have nowhere to go. The Sword Sisters who pick them up are experienced riders and use the art of warfare to protect themselves and create some kind of 'womenrights' movement, to stop the oppression of women. Though many of the girls decide to leave after a while due to some complications with their leader and use their skills in other ways, such as enlisting in mercenary companies or even in the armies of the kings. This makes it hard for the head of the Sword Sisters, to grow their community and to follow their main goal.">
