           name="{=InFa.fac_expedition}Calradi Expedition"
           tier="4"
           text="{=InFa.fac_expedition.desc}The Calradi Expedition is a group of fanatic believers who think of themselves as the chosen people to bring peace, in the way of war. They were sent from different lands into Calradia to establish themselves, bring some sort of order and peace to these lands and anyone who would stand against them in their journey, would get killed. Though, as time has passed they have lost a lot of power, as their connections to their homes got cut off by the strong powers in Calradia. Now with the loss of majority of their power, many of their once so 'loyal' adherents left. Today, many of the members who still feel themselves bound to the order, got skeptical if their leader was really a 'chosen one' who should be leading the expedition.">
